In Chat in version 3.2.4 Bugs in activating Voice Video call start buttons while recording a voicemail and ending voicemail recording Bug when Voice Video call start buttons are active when the profile screen is entered when a voice call is received Bug when call bar appears when trying to open a message by swiping the notification A total of 6 different bugs have been fixed including the simultaneous playback of Video and Audio message.

In Chat in version 3.2.3 Bugs related to call audio video on the routing screen have been fixed. The bug of opening the call evaluation notification on other screens has been fixed. Bugs that cause the icon and seen status of the last messages disappear from the interface in the Chats tab have been fixed. The text of the back button on the call notification screen has been corrected. The bug of sending feedback with space character has been fixed. The interface bug of the date section in the Chats tab has been fixed. A total of 8 different bugs have been fixed.

In Chat in version 3.2.2 User interface bugs have been fixed on the routing screen. iOS 16 compatibility improvements. The bug of the application not returning to portrait mode has been fixed. The bug that the leave button does not appear when the person who left is added on the group information screen has been fixed. A total of 5 different bugs have been fixed.
In Chat in version 3.2.1 Security updates. iOS 16 compatibility improvements. Contact sharing issue fixed. A total of 4 different bugs have been fixed.

In Chat in version 3.2.0 The bug of opening the chats screen without registering in the application has been fixed. The bug of opening the registration screen incorrectly while using the application has been fixed. The freezing bug on the membership screen has been fixed. Various interface improvements have been made within the application.
Fixed an error when forwarding photos and videos.

In Chat in version 3.1.5 Improvements have been made in the message forwarding process and various bugs have been fixed. Various bugs that occurred during location sharing have been fixed.
